{"segment_id": "laozi-chapter-068__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531__seg-001", "work_id": "laozi", "section_id": "laozi-chapter-068", "source_id": "laozi-chapter-068__chinesenotes-daodejing-zh-20260531", "language": "zh-Hant", "segment_type": "chapter", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "老子 68", "sort_key": "068.000", "text_original": "善為士者不武，\n\n善戰者不怒，\n\n善勝敵者不與，\n\n善用人者為之下，是謂不爭之德，是謂用人之力，\n\n是謂配天古之極。", "text_normalized": "善為士者不武，\n\n善戰者不怒，\n\n善勝敵者不與，\n\n善用人者為之下，是謂不爭之德，是謂用人之力，\n\n是謂配天古之極。", "notes": ""}
